OL,7,FFrench authorities have banned
OL,8,FTelegram co-founder Pavel Durov from
OL,9,Fleaving the country and have issued
OL,10,Fpreliminary charges over alleged
OL,11,Fcriminal activity on his messaging app.
OL,13,FDurov was detained at an airport
OL,14,Foutside of Paris as part of a sweeping
OL,15,Finvestigation and was later released
OL,16,Fafter four days of questioning.
