OL,7,FInvestigative judges filed preliminary
OL,8,Fcharges when on Wednesday, ordering
OL,9,Fhim to pay E5 million euros (#4.2
OL,10,Fmillion) bail and report to a police
OL,11,Fstation twice a week.
OL,13,FThe allegations against Russian-born
OL,14,FDurov, a French citizen, include that
OL,15,Fhis platform is being used for child
OL,16,Fsexual abuse and drug trafficking.
OL,18,FIt also includes allegations that
OL,19,FTelegram refused to share information
OL,20,For documents with investigators when
OL,21,Frequired by law.
