OL,7,FHis arrest has caused outrage in
OL,8,FRussia, with some government officials
OL,9,Fcalling it politically motivated and
OL,10,Faccused the West of a double standard
OL,11,Fon freedom of speech.
OL,13,FThe outcry has raised eyebrows among
OL,14,FKremlin critics because in 2018,
OL,15,FRussian authorities themselves tried
OL,16,Fto block the Telegram app but failed,
OL,17,Fwithdrawing the ban in 2020.
