OL,7,FFrench President Emmanuel Macron said
OL,8,FMonday that Durov's arrest wasn't a
OL,9,Fpolitical move but part of an
OL,10,Findependent investigation.
OL,12,FMacron posted on X that his country
OL,13,F"is deeply committed" to freedom of
OL,14,Fexpression but "freedoms are upheld
OL,15,Fwithin a legal framework, both on
OL,16,Fsocial media and in real life, to
OL,17,Fprotect citizens and respect their
OL,18,Ffundamental rights".
