OL,7,FIn 2013, he sold his stake in
OL,8,FVKontakte, a popular Russian social
OL,9,Fnetworking site which he launched in
OL,10,F2006.
OL,12,FThe company came under pressure during
OL,13,Fthe Russian government's crackdown
OL,14,Ffollowing mass pro-democracy protests
OL,15,Fthat rocked Moscow at the end of 2011
OL,16,Fand 2012.
