OL,7,FDurov had said authorities demanded
OL,8,Fthat the site take down online
OL,9,Fcommunities of Russian opposition
OL,10,Factivists, and later that it hand over
OL,11,Fpersonal data of users who took part
OL,12,Fin the 2013-2014 popular uprising in
