OL,7,FThe demonstrations prompted Russian
OL,8,Fauthorities to clamp down on the
OL,9,Fdigital space, and Telegram and its
OL,10,Fpro-privacy rhetoric offered a
OL,11,Fconvenient way for Russians to
OL,12,Fcommunicate and share news.
OL,14,FTelegram also continues to be a
OL,15,Fpopular source of news in Ukraine,
OL,16,Fwhere both media outlets and officials
OL,17,Fuse it to share information on the
OL,18,Fwar, and deliver missile and air raid
OL,19,Falerts.
